      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- saves all chat pages\nincluding private and\ngrouped.\n- it has several parts like:\nid, name, is_group,\ncreated_at",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- saves all chat pages including private and grouped.\n- it has several parts like:  id, name, is_group, created_at",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "MSAAuVN1b_r8xc_-JTKJ9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 833,
      "y": 75,
      "width": 202.07299804687494,
      "height": 172.8,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
